item.title: What Have We Accomplished
item.description: We have: Structured a Node.js serverless application code following best practices. Deployed an application consisting of serverless microservices using AWS SAM. Created a multi-environment CI/CD Pipeline for serverless applications. Deployed our Code and Pipeline as a reusable asset across an entire organization.
